# Icons to be generated separately.
#
# Required sizes (per public/manifest.json):
#   - 192x192 px  (standard PWA icon)
#   - 512x512 px  (PWA splash / install)
#   - 512x512 px maskable (safe-zone crop for Android adaptive icons)
#
# Generation options:
#   1. https://maskable.app/editor  — maskable variant
#   2. https://realfavicongenerator.net — all sizes from one source SVG
#   3. `npx pwa-asset-generator <source.svg> public/icons`
#
# File names expected by manifest.json:
#   icon-192.png
#   icon-512.png
#   icon-512-maskable.png
#
# See public/manifest.json for the full icons array.
